{"type":"message","id":"d5042365","parentId":"bb76e9b7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:07.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron-triggered task for real-time stock price monitoring. I need to read the configuration file to understand what tasks need to be executed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58563382bb1542148e7c0c03","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773119100078}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7cf0d6e","parentId":"d5042365","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:07.212Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_58563382bb1542148e7c0c03","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 你的工作路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 自定义文件路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock\n- 你独享的skill存放位置：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/skills\n- 以下描述中没有具体位置的文件都是自定义文件，存放在自定义路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 指定了具体路径的文件，按照指定路径读取，如：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md；\n- 如果你需要新建文件，统一存放在自定义路径下；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119107211}}
{"type":"message","id":"2269bc6b","parentId":"e7cf0d6e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read several configuration files to understand the complete workflow: tushare-data skill usage, get-data-template.md, alert-rules.md, receiver-list.txt, and alert-template.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5728c2d4db5487babdb5fa1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0112a1f0542e407ca8d36bdd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bb042669fdfe414d9af464c8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9898c174a884448c8e6068f7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b65707e565134d928c10a1f0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773119107212}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9c508de","parentId":"2269bc6b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.438Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d5728c2d4db5487babdb5fa1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119113437}}
{"type":"message","id":"9356425b","parentId":"b9c508de","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.441Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0112a1f0542e407ca8d36bdd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119113439}}
{"type":"message","id":"30140ac5","parentId":"9356425b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.443Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bb042669fdfe414d9af464c8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\nou_0737da20bef21e4dff04d2b83f927208\nou_144623d3a3b4a119305355db7813bb31\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119113442}}
{"type":"message","id":"19804823","parentId":"30140ac5","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9898c174a884448c8e6068f7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119113444}}
{"type":"message","id":"10ec8e13","parentId":"19804823","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:05:13.448Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b65707e565134d928c10a1f0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## 你的工作区~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 所有的技能操作都只能在这个工作区下进行\n- 包括创建文件、删除文件、修改文件\n- 如果有skill要求你在~/下操作，统一重定向到~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n\n## 固定文件位置\n- 我的自选股全部维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt下，相关操作统一在此维护\n- 预警规则维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md，相关操作统一在此文件中维护\n\n\n## 常用技能速查\n\n### 股票分析\n- 优先使用tushare-data skill获取数据,tushare_token已经配置在环境变量里，可通过env获取\n- 实时数据定义：最近1-2分钟内的数据\n- 进行涨跌分析时，注意要获取实时数据,参考https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374，学习如何使用实时数据接口\n- 以下是获取实时数据的一系列接口文档，严格参考接口文档获取数据：\n -- 实时分钟：https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374  \n -- 每个可调用的接口都优先使用批量获取参数，如：ts_code字段支持单个和多个（600000.SH 或者 600000.SH,000001.SZ），优先使用多个参数的调用方式，防止限流\n- 数据要多方对比，确保准确性和时效性\n- 回复数据时务必表明数据来源\n- 如果出现接口访问不通的情况，使用浏览器打开同花顺，获取对应股票数据，整理后返回结构化数据\n- 回复模版参考~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md\n\n## 禁忌\n- 不要自行定义脚本\n- 不允许在工作空间外操作数据 \n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773119113447}}
